originalText.text: So thankful for this garage! Nice wide entrance. Can book a spot through SpotHero. Friendly staff. Car always ready to pick up according to booking window (I’ve never waited more than 5 mins for it to come up).

text.text: So thankful for this garage! Nice wide entrance. Can book a spot through SpotHero. Friendly staff. Car always ready to pick up according to booking window (I’ve never waited more than 5 mins for it to come up).

originalText.text: Had a reservation with this place for a couple days. You drive down park it like the instructions say. They scan your reservation and then you get a receipt and you leave! Alot of reviews saying the employees are rude, they are not rude they just don't speak English, but they are hard at work!!! Got my car back with my receipt and maybe a simple 5 minute wait time. No scratches, no dings, and it was how I left it.

originalText.text: If you absolutely must use this place, make sure you inspect your vehicle very closely before you leave. They left small scratches on my brand-new vehicle! When I pointed them out, the attendant had the nerve to ask if it was just a rental. When there is a problem, they have a claim form, but make  sure you document any issues yourself, with your own camera, which I did.
